Browser Runtime Static Rendering Browser Runtime Static Rendering The browser runtime fixture covers static DOM parsing, simple CSS display handling, link extraction, and text layout. This page is intentionally small, deterministic, and suitable for smoke tests without network access. brutal searchBrutal Search Rust Crawler Brutal Search Rust Crawler Brutal search crawls static HTML, extracts text, builds a Rust inverted index, and renders plain text results quickly. The crawler fixture links to the browser runtime and Chromium benchmark pages so authority scoring has a tiny graph. browser runtime chromium benchmarkChromium Benchmark Gate Chromium Benchmark Gate The Chromium benchmark fixture helps verify reproducible reports, p95 latency metrics, throughput, corpus hash, and index hash output. The benchmark smoke command proves the local index can be built, searched, rendered, and measured from one command. rust crawlerSpeedtest by Ookla - The Global Broadband Speed Test English العربية Deutsch English Español Français Bahasa Indonesia Italiano 日本語 한국어 Nederlands Polski Português Русский Svenska ไทย 中文(简体) 中文(繁體) Apps Android Apple TV iOS macOS Windows Learn Glossary Guides FAQ Data Ookla Research ™ Speedtest Awards ™ Speedtest Global Index ™ Speedtest Performance Directory ™ About Apps Methodology Press Ookla Advertise HELP Results History Settings Help Create Account English العربية Deutsch English Español Français Bahasa Indonesia Italiano 日本語 한국어 Nederlands Polski Português Русский Svenska ไทย 中文(简体) 中文(繁體) Go Remove Speedtest.net Ads Speedtest ® Account Advertise Speedtest Awards ™ Speedtest Servers ™ Speedtest Performance Directory ™ Ziff Davis Ookla ® Brands Downdetector® Ekahau® RootMetrics® Apps Android Apple TV iOS macOS Windows © 2006-2026 Ookla, LLC., a Ziff Davis company. All Rights Reserved. Ookla ® , Speedtest ® , and Speedtest Intelligence ® are among the federally registered trademarks of Ookla, LLC and may only be used with explicit written permis