. (1996). "Endangered freshwater fish of Spain". Conservation of Endangered Freshwater Fish in Europe . pp. 55– 61. doi : 10.1007/978-3-0348-9014-4_6 . ISBN 978-3-0348-9867-6 . Elvira, B. (February 1995). "Native and exotic freshwater fishes in Spanish river basins". Freshwater Biology . 33 (1): 103– 108. Bibcode : 1995FrBio..33..103E . doi : 10.1111/j.1365-2427.1995.tb00390.x . Elvira, B.; Almodovar, A. (December 2001). "Freshwater fish introductions in Spain: facts and figures at the beginning of the 21st century". Journal of Fish Biology . 59 : 323– 331. Bibcode : 2001JFBio..59S.323E . doi : 10.1111/j.1095-8649.2001.tb01393.x . Elvira, Benigno (1995). "Conservation status of endemic freshwater fish in Spain". Biological Conservation . 72 (2): 129– 136. Bibcode : 1995BCons..72..129E . doi : 10.1016/0006-3207(94)00076-3 . Garcia-Marin, J.L.; Jorde, P.E.; Ryman, N.; Utter, F.; Pla, C. (June 1991). "Management implications of genetic differentiation between native and hatchery populations of brown trout (Salmo trutta) in Spain". Aquaculture . 95 ( 3– 4): 235– 249. Bibcode : 1991Aquac..95..235G . doi : 10.1016/0044-8486(91)90090-T . Retrieved from " https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Freshwater_fish_of_Spain&oldid=1338041619 " Category : Freshwater fish by country Hidden categories: Articles with short description Short description with empty Wikidata description Articles lacking in-text citations from July 2021 All articles lacking in-text citations This page was last edited on 12 February 2026, at 22:11 (UTC) . Text is available under the Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 License ; additional terms may apply. By using this site, you agree to the Terms of Use and Privacy Policy . Wikipedia® is a registered trademark of the Wikimedia Foundation, Inc. , a non-profit organization. Privacy policy About Wikipedia Disclaimers Contact Wikipedia Legal & safety contacts Code of Conduct Developers Statistics Cookie statement Mobile view Search Search Toggle t