g more than fourfold. The rates of women... Hantavirus remains extremely rare in the US — but severe when it occurs Estrogen-based hormone replacement therapy use is rising Find more research Featured in Visit the newsroom Follow us on LinkedIn to keep up with the latest from Truveta Follow us Ready to accelerate your research with representative, complete, and real-time data? Truveta Data Truveta Intelligence Truveta Evidence Research Resources News Careers Privacy notice Contact us © Truveta 2026 &times; Interested in learning more? Our website uses cookies to ensure you have the best experience. Accept Privacy notice